<ul><li>Owing to the <b>shorter wavelength</b>&nbsp;in the laser they use, this creates&nbsp;<b>much smaller pits</b>.</li><li>Enabling a&nbsp;<b>greater number</b>&nbsp;to fit in the same space along the track.</li><li>The track can also be&nbsp;<b>more tightly wound</b>, therefore much longer.</li></ul>